      <title>构建智能客服大脑：一个链式处理AI Agent的实践与思考</title>
      <link>https://blog.jaxiu.cn/blog/2025-07/%E6%9E%84%E5%BB%BA%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E5%AE%A2%E6%9C%8D%E5%A4%A7%E8%84%91%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E9%93%BE%E5%BC%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86ai-agent%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5%E4%B8%8E%E6%80%9D%E8%80%83/</link>
